Product_Title: Push-Up Board with Resistance Bands and Exercise Guide Pulsher
Body_Html:
Get in shape with InnovaGoods and their new sport and fitness items, such as the Push-Up Board with Resistance Bands and Exercise Guide Pulsher InnovaGoods! Discover a wide range of high-quality products that stand out due to their functionality, efficiency and innovative design. Ideal for improving your shape and fitness!

A comprehensive workout system with removable exercise board, grips, resistance bands and exercise guide. Ideal for exercising the entire body. The board highlights exercises for 4 muscle groups: chest, shoulders, back and triceps, the chest exercise being the most widely recognised. The rubber bands can be used for the arm exercises (mainly biceps) and for legs (mainly glutes). The intensity of the exercise can be controlled by adjusting the size of the elastic bands with the help of the metal hooks on the base.

  • Material:

    • polypropylene
  • Colour:

Product_Title: AMZER Shockproof Glitter Powder TPU Protective
Body_Html:
This TPU case for the iPhone XI has a back panel that is all glittered up for maximum impact. This eye-catching phone case has a bold but still effortlessly classy look that is perfect in any setting. The glitter case is crafted from top quality TPU plastic that is soft and flexible but sturdy and guaranteed to last a long time. The case holds your iPhone XI in a snug grip and covers it from the back, sides, top, and bottom. Made from strong but flexible thermoplastic polyurethane, the glittery protective case keeps your iPhone XI safe from dirt, rain, dust, and scratches. The material is naturally impact-resistant and absorbs shock from bumps and falls.


Features:

  • Simple, comfortable, easy to carry.
  • Sophisticated case complemented by radiant sparkles for a complete luxe-look.
  • Quite slim and lightweight design.
  • It protects your device from the normal scratches, dirt, tear and wear.
  • All buttons and ports are easy to access without removing the case.
  • Flexible wrap-around TPU case offers comfortable grip and easy installation.
  • Slim and compact design provides a snug fit to your device.
  • Built-in covered power and volume button for extra protection.

Specification:

Product Type: TPU Case.

Manufacturer: AMZER.

Product_Title: Shell Ejection Foam Darts Pistol Soft Bullet Toy Gun
Body_Html:
Shell ejection + shooting, perfectly restore the real pistol shooting process.
This is a blowback pistol which means the slide moves back when you Press the trigger.
When there is no bullet in the toy, the slide will be locked when the trigger is pressed, Last round bolt hold open.
Safe & Durable:This Toy Pistol is made of high-quality ABS material, the barrel is alloy material.
Perfect Gift:This cool toy pistol is very realistic in looks. The great holiday, Birthday gifts for 5+ year old boys.

 1 * gun

6* shells

Product_Title: Eye Care Massager USB Rechargeable - Wireless Pressure Vibration
Body_Html:
Rechargeable Magnetic Eye Massager AR 018 is quickly charged via USB to easily carry and use this device at your own convenience and comfort.This portable device allows to take care of you eye health anywhere you may be.

Designed to work on acupuncture points massage vibration massage modes, and magnetic therapy to promote the blood circulation of the eye skin, enhance the elasticity, relieve eyes fatigue, dilute dark circles, remove eye patch, wrinkles and other eye problems.

It automatically runs through 9 massage modes for approximately 5 minutes. 

It uses 22 finger shaped massage contacts, made of high-purity silicone, and neodymium medical magnets to effectively help relieve eye tension, bags, wrinkles and restore healthy eye power.

Potential Benefits

  • Can effectively prevent eye myopia, remove bags under the eyes, wrinkles, dark circles, and enhance skin elasticity.
  • May Improve blood circulation eliminate eye strain and muscle tension
  • Relax muscles to reduce insomnia
  • The natural health magnet can quickly activate the magnetic field of human body and restore healthy power
  • Beautify eyes
  • Increase elasticity

Features

  • Combines silicone and magnet material, safe and effective.
  • The massager is carefully designed according to the high and low contours of the eye and the distribution of the different acupoints.
  • Suitable for anyone who may excessively use their eyes
  • Rechargeable 
  • Smart touch screen
  • Wireless design
  • Multi frequency vibration
  • 22 neodymium magnetic massage nodes
  • Allows 1hr of massage once charges
  • Switches off automatically after approximately 5 minutes of massage

Specifications

  • Smart Touch Screen to turn on/off
  • Material: ABS
  • Color: Black + White
  • Size: approx. 19cm x 6.5cm
  • On/Off touch screen 
  • Adjustable elastic band, suitable for most people
  • A small motor controlled by a computer IC chip that produces the desired massage effect at different speeds
  • 22 neodymium magnetic contact points
  • Automatically runs through 9 massage modes, lasting approximately 15 seconds for each mode -
  1. Automatic
  2. Strong Gear 
  3. Medium Gear
  4. Weak
  5. Tenderly
  6. Comfort
  7. Strong beat
  8. Medium Beat
  9. Fast Beat

Package includes

  • 1x Eye Care Massager (foam protected) in cardboard package
  • 1 x USB Charger and AU Adapter Plug
  • 1x User's Manual (on box)
  • 2x Neodymium Magnets
  • 1x Eye Test Chart

Product_Title: Amzer Apple MFi Certified 2-1 Sync & Charge Lightning cable with micro
Body_Html:
Multiple device owners rejoice! Charge and Sync all of your devices with one cable! A lightning connector for your latest Apple iOS device. And a micro USB connector for your eReaders, Bluetooth devices, headsets and more. Micro USB connector easily attaches to the Lightning connector for your choice in charging. Charge your devices through any USB port at home or on the go and connect to your computer for easy syncing and data transfer. This 2-in-1 cable is perfect for your on the go lifestyle!


MORE INFORMATION

 

Features:

  • Charge your devices through any USB port at home or in your vehicle.
  • Connect to your computer for easy syncing and data transfer.
  • The standard micro USB cable connects to smartphones, Bluetooth speakers, headsets, eReaders, power banks, and more.
  • Conveniently switch between a micro USB and Lightning cable.
  • Cable measures 1M or 3.2 ft.
  • Cable OD measures 3 mm.
  • Lightning cable is a reversible design.
  • 2-in-1 USB charge and sync cable.

Specification:

  • MFi certified.
  • Product Type: Data Sync & Charge Cable.
  • Material: TPE material.
  • Length: 1M or 3.2 ft.
  • Manufacturer: AMZER.

Product_Title: 220V LED Neon Flex Rope Strip Green colour Light Sign Outdoor
AMZER Shockproof Rugged Silicone Skin Jelly Case for Apple iPad mini
Body_Html:
The Amzer® Black Jelly Case is made out of 100% premium silicone and is a great, light-weight option for protecting your iPad Mini. The durable silicone absorbs any shock your iPad Mini may receive from any accidental drops or bumps, keeping it just like new. A double layer of silicone protects the corners and back of your iP! The textured silicone to the sides ensures a lasting grip on your iPad and minimizes sliding on flat surfaces. The featured silicone button over your home button delivers precise control and added protection! You have full access to your iPad Mini without removing it from the case. The Jelly Case is truly like a second skin and a must have accessory!
Note : Does Not Support iPad mini 3 With Touch ID.


MORE INFORMATION

 

AMZER Product Review:

Overview: The AMZER Silicone Skin Cover is a great option for anyone who is looking for great protection for their Apple iPad mini that is a breeze to use, while still providing excellent coverage, design, durability and usage.

Durability: Being cast out of a single piece of durable formulated silicone, the cover is very resilient. It has very little give which gives it an excellent grip on the Apple iPad mini which helps prevents it from getting caught on things; but even so, the durable material isnt likely to tear unless cut with a blade or stretched heavily. And even when it is strained, stretched, or pinched it snaps back instantaneously without losing its original form or durability.

Typical damage wise, its very resilient with the exception of sharp slices. Blunt object, jabs and scratches turned up no damage; but it will show cuts from sharp instruments. So just keep it away from the scissors or the cutting board at home and you shouldnt have any problems.

Design/Functionality: Well, unless it installed itself, it couldnt be easier to attach to your Apple iPad mini; you just stretch it a bit and pop the Apple iPad mini in and you are done. The silicone is molded extremely well has cut outs or raised buttons, ensuring that all your devices features are easily usable. In addition, the silicon’s shape grips the edges of your Apple iPad mini, giving it a very firm hold on the Tablet. As well as preventing it from getting caught on things and potentially tearing, this also prevents the infiltration of small particulates around the Apple iPad mini which can eventually cause damage via friction. The excellent grip on the Tablet, combined with the material also provides an excellent grip on your Apple iPad mini, preventing the most common cause of Tablet injury, drops.

The single piece, flexible material is also extremely good at absorbing and distributing damage across its surface; preventing cracks and other damage that occur due to a high impact at a single point. Additionally, it is extremely lightweight and the great form factor prevents it from being bulky or adding much girth to the device as well as coming in a variety of colors.

Conclusion: This is a great cover if youre looking for something that gives you a great fit along with great durability.

Features:

  • Fashionable & flexible AMZER Jelly Cover for your new Apple iPad mini!
  • The AMZER Jelly Covers are made from durable premium silicone.
  • Protect your Apple iPad mini from accidental bumps.
  • Provides a firm grip and prevents your Apple iPad mini from sliding across your cars dashboard or angled surfaces.
  • It’s special anti-dust and scratch-free properties, preserves your Tablet shining look.
  • Quality material used for this skin provides shield and avoid scratches.
  • Helps to prevent your device from sliding on soft surfaces or angle surfaces.
  • The revolutionary technology keeps dust away from the cover.
  • Precise cutouts give easy access to all the functionalities.
  • This elegant skin-tight jelly cover is perfectly manufactured to fit.
  • Installation and removal are very easy.
  • Protect your new Apple iPad mini at all times.
  • Available in different colors to match your personality and thought.
  • Silicone button over home key delivers precise control every time and added protection.

Specifications:

  • Type: Silicone Skin Jelly Case.
  • Material: Premium silicone material.
  • Length: 8.125 inches.
  • Width: 5.625 inches.
  • Thickness: 0.5 inches. 
  • Manufacturer: AMZER.

Product_Title: AMZER Shockproof Rugged Silicone Skin Jelly Case for Apple iPad mini
Body_Html:
The Amzer® Black Jelly Case is made out of 100% premium silicone and is a great, light-weight option for protecting your iPad Mini. The durable silicone absorbs any shock your iPad Mini may receive from any accidental drops or bumps, keeping it just like new. A double layer of silicone protects the corners and back of your iP! The textured silicone to the sides ensures a lasting grip on your iPad and minimizes sliding on flat surfaces. The featured silicone button over your home button delivers precise control and added protection! You have full access to your iPad Mini without removing it from the case. The Jelly Case is truly like a second skin and a must have accessory!
Note : Does Not Support iPad mini 3 With Touch ID.


MORE INFORMATION

 

AMZER Product Review:

Overview: The AMZER Silicone Skin Cover is a great option for anyone who is looking for great protection for their Apple iPad mini that is a breeze to use, while still providing excellent coverage, design, durability and usage.

Durability: Being cast out of a single piece of durable formulated silicone, the cover is very resilient. It has very little give which gives it an excellent grip on the Apple iPad mini which helps prevents it from getting caught on things; but even so, the durable material isnt likely to tear unless cut with a blade or stretched heavily. And even when it is strained, stretched, or pinched it snaps back instantaneously without losing its original form or durability.

Typical damage wise, its very resilient with the exception of sharp slices. Blunt object, jabs and scratches turned up no damage; but it will show cuts from sharp instruments. So just keep it away from the scissors or the cutting board at home and you shouldnt have any problems.

Design/Functionality: Well, unless it installed itself, it couldnt be easier to attach to your Apple iPad mini; you just stretch it a bit and pop the Apple iPad mini in and you are done. The silicone is molded extremely well has cut outs or raised buttons, ensuring that all your devices features are easily usable. In addition, the silicon’s shape grips the edges of your Apple iPad mini, giving it a very firm hold on the Tablet. As well as preventing it from getting caught on things and potentially tearing, this also prevents the infiltration of small particulates around the Apple iPad mini which can eventually cause damage via friction. The excellent grip on the Tablet, combined with the material also provides an excellent grip on your Apple iPad mini, preventing the most common cause of Tablet injury, drops.

The single piece, flexible material is also extremely good at absorbing and distributing damage across its surface; preventing cracks and other damage that occur due to a high impact at a single point. Additionally, it is extremely lightweight and the great form factor prevents it from being bulky or adding much girth to the device as well as coming in a variety of colors.

Conclusion: This is a great cover if youre looking for something that gives you a great fit along with great durability.

Features:

  • Fashionable & flexible AMZER Jelly Cover for your new Apple iPad mini!
  • The AMZER Jelly Covers are made from durable premium silicone.
  • Protect your Apple iPad mini from accidental bumps.
  • Provides a firm grip and prevents your Apple iPad mini from sliding across your cars dashboard or angled surfaces.
  • It’s special anti-dust and scratch-free properties, preserves your Tablet shining look.
  • Quality material used for this skin provides shield and avoid scratches.
  • Helps to prevent your device from sliding on soft surfaces or angle surfaces.
  • The revolutionary technology keeps dust away from the cover.
  • Precise cutouts give easy access to all the functionalities.
  • This elegant skin-tight jelly cover is perfectly manufactured to fit.
  • Installation and removal are very easy.
  • Protect your new Apple iPad mini at all times.
  • Available in different colors to match your personality and thought.
  • Silicone button over home key delivers precise control every time and added protection.

Specifications:

  • Type: Silicone Skin Jelly Case.
  • Material: Premium silicone material.
  • Length: 8.125 inches.
  • Width: 5.625 inches.
  • Thickness: 0.5 inches. 
  • Manufacturer: AMZER.

Product_Title: AMZER Shockproof Rugged Silicone Skin Jelly Case for Apple iPad mini
Body_Html:
The Amzer® Black Jelly Case is made out of 100% premium silicone and is a great, light-weight option for protecting your iPad Mini. The durable silicone absorbs any shock your iPad Mini may receive from any accidental drops or bumps, keeping it just like new. A double layer of silicone protects the corners and back of your iP! The textured silicone to the sides ensures a lasting grip on your iPad and minimizes sliding on flat surfaces. The featured silicone button over your home button delivers precise control and added protection! You have full access to your iPad Mini without removing it from the case. The Jelly Case is truly like a second skin and a must have accessory!
Note : Does Not Support iPad mini 3 With Touch ID.


MORE INFORMATION

 

AMZER Product Review:

Overview: The AMZER Silicone Skin Cover is a great option for anyone who is looking for great protection for their Apple iPad mini that is a breeze to use, while still providing excellent coverage, design, durability and usage.

Durability: Being cast out of a single piece of durable formulated silicone, the cover is very resilient. It has very little give which gives it an excellent grip on the Apple iPad mini which helps prevents it from getting caught on things; but even so, the durable material isnt likely to tear unless cut with a blade or stretched heavily. And even when it is strained, stretched, or pinched it snaps back instantaneously without losing its original form or durability.

Typical damage wise, its very resilient with the exception of sharp slices. Blunt object, jabs and scratches turned up no damage; but it will show cuts from sharp instruments. So just keep it away from the scissors or the cutting board at home and you shouldnt have any problems.

Design/Functionality: Well, unless it installed itself, it couldnt be easier to attach to your Apple iPad mini; you just stretch it a bit and pop the Apple iPad mini in and you are done. The silicone is molded extremely well has cut outs or raised buttons, ensuring that all your devices features are easily usable. In addition, the silicon’s shape grips the edges of your Apple iPad mini, giving it a very firm hold on the Tablet. As well as preventing it from getting caught on things and potentially tearing, this also prevents the infiltration of small particulates around the Apple iPad mini which can eventually cause damage via friction. The excellent grip on the Tablet, combined with the material also provides an excellent grip on your Apple iPad mini, preventing the most common cause of Tablet injury, drops.

The single piece, flexible material is also extremely good at absorbing and distributing damage across its surface; preventing cracks and other damage that occur due to a high impact at a single point. Additionally, it is extremely lightweight and the great form factor prevents it from being bulky or adding much girth to the device as well as coming in a variety of colors.

Conclusion: This is a great cover if youre looking for something that gives you a great fit along with great durability.

Features:

  • Fashionable & flexible AMZER Jelly Cover for your new Apple iPad mini!
  • The AMZER Jelly Covers are made from durable premium silicone.
  • Protect your Apple iPad mini from accidental bumps.
  • Provides a firm grip and prevents your Apple iPad mini from sliding across your cars dashboard or angled surfaces.
  • It’s special anti-dust and scratch-free properties, preserves your Tablet shining look.
  • Quality material used for this skin provides shield and avoid scratches.
  • Helps to prevent your device from sliding on soft surfaces or angle surfaces.
  • The revolutionary technology keeps dust away from the cover.
  • Precise cutouts give easy access to all the functionalities.
  • This elegant skin-tight jelly cover is perfectly manufactured to fit.
  • Installation and removal are very easy.
  • Protect your new Apple iPad mini at all times.
  • Available in different colors to match your personality and thought.
  • Silicone button over home key delivers precise control every time and added protection.

Product_Title: AMZER Ultra Hybrid SlimGrip Case for iPhone 12 Pro Max With Clear
Body_Html:
CLEARLY this is the case you've been searching for! Sleek and minimal, it's protection with a crystal-clear view to your iPhone 12 Pro Max. Transparent impact resistant hybrid casing with a durable TPU bumper protects against impact from falls and bumps. TPU buttons protecting the volume and power for a little extra coverage. Cutouts for all ports and controls for instant access and the bezel surrounding your screen is extended for a lay flat design, allowing you to place the phone face-down without the screen touching the tabletop!

MORE INFORMATION

Features of iPhone 12 Pro Max Hybrid SlimGrip Case:

Features:

  • Provides excellent protection for your iPhone 12 Pro Max.
  • Quality material used for this hybrid case to provide a shield and avoid scratches.
  • The smooth outer back shell provides sure grip to keep your iPhone 12 Pro Max from dropped or bumped.
  • Precise cutouts give easy access to all the functionalities.
  • Precisely engineered includes custom cut-outs to fit your iPhone 12 Pro Max perfectly.
  • Plug your charger, cable or headset without removing the case.

Specification:

  • Product Type: SlimGrip Hybrid Case.
  • Manufacturer: AMZER.

Product_Title: Squishy Face Studio Super Tug Dog Toy
Body_Html:
For The Strong Dog Guardian - Finally, A Safe, Easy, And Painless Way To Play Tug-Of-War

  • Perfect for people with strong dogs who like to play tug-of-war but don’t like having dislocated shoulders.
  • Durable polyester Tug is soft on your dog’s mouth and is safer than rope tugs which have easily ingested rope strands.
  • 2” wide polypropylene webbing strap has the strength of heavy chain without causing damage to tree bark.
  • Super strong marine grade bungee cord eliminates the need for a metal spring.
  • “Perfection Loops” tied at the ends of the bungee cord eliminate extra connectors and only become tighter with use.
  • Designed to hold up to the most powerful dogs but will still work with dogs of any size.
  • Great for people with limited mobility.
  • Also works great as a training tool and provides the mental exercise dogs need at the same time they are getting physical exercise.
  • Replacement Tugs and bungee cord sections available for purchase.
  • Strap is long enough to wrap around trees up to approximately 94" in circumference.

Tug-of-war is a game that dogs naturally love to play and can be great exercise. If you have a powerful dog like I do, you know what happens to your arm and shoulder after a few minutes of playing. Ouch!

Looking for a solution to this problem, I read about something called a "spring pole". A spring pole involves using a large metal spring to suspend a rope from an overhead tree branch with a toy hanging from the end. Then the dog can hang, shake, and tug against the resistance of the spring. I made one for our high energy pit bull dogs and they loved it. Unfortunately, I quickly found some serious design flaws that ended up causing an injury (thankfully minor) to Maxwell, our company mascot.

So I designed the Super Tug, a safer alternative to the spring pole. It uses a horizontal configuration instead of the vertical one seen with traditional spring pole designs. It also uses super strong, marine grade bungee cord instead of a metal spring. The connection points are designed so that in case of failure, nothing comes flying back towards your dog.

These dog toys are made in the USA using components tested for durability, strength, and safety.

Product_Title: AMZER ShatterProof Screen Protector for iPhone 12 Pro Max - Front
Body_Html:
AMZER ShatterProof Screen Protector is super thin urethane film at only 0.2 mm thick, ShatterProof certified by the ASTM (American Society for Testing and Materials) having passed D1004 Tear Strength, D2240 Hardness and D4329 UV Light Discoloration Tests. The protector is scratch resistant, stress resistant, drop resistant and has a special self healing capability with dissipative functioning embodied - it is virtually indestructible making your iPhone 12 Pro Max unbreakable!. The AMZER ShatterProof Screen Protector is a revolutionary product innovated to provide the best protection to the next-generation of wireless devices. AMZER ShatterProof Screen Protector's extreme grade protection making the iPhone shatter and shock proof. ShatterProof has a unique shock dissipative function - unlike any other product in it's category - ShatterProof uses the physics concept of dissipation, dissipation embodies the concept of a dynamical system where important mechanical modes, such as waves or oscillations, lose energy over time. ShatterProof does exactly the same to protect devices from drops and shocks, drops and stress which wireless devices usually don't survive - which is why the name ShatterProof.

MORE INFORMATION

Features of iPhone 12 Pro Max ShatterProof Screen Protector:

Features:

  • Protects your iPhone 12 Pro Max from impacts and dirt and dust.
  • Provides extreme grade protection to your iPhone 12 Pro Max.
  • Its Shock Dissipative Function allows your device to withstand extreme shock and pressure.
  • Scratch Resistance.
  • Easy Application thanks to the silicon adhesion.
  • Self Healing Properties deliver resistance to damage.

Product_Title: AMZER Shockproof Glitter Powder TPU Protective
Body_Html:
This TPU case for the iPhone XIR has a back panel that is all glittered up for maximum impact. This eye-catching phone case has a bold but still effortlessly classy look that is perfect in any setting. The glitter case is crafted from top quality TPU plastic that is soft and flexible but sturdy and guaranteed to last a long time. The case holds your iPhone XIR in a snug grip and covers it from the back, sides, top, and bottom. Made from strong but flexible thermoplastic polyurethane, the glittery protective case keeps your iPhone XIR safe from dirt, rain, dust, and scratches. The material is naturally impact-resistant and absorbs shock from bumps and falls.


Features:

  • Simple, comfortable, easy to carry.
  • Sophisticated case complemented by radiant sparkles for a complete luxe-look.
  • Quite slim and lightweight design.
  • It protects your device from the normal scratches, dirt, tear and wear.
  • All buttons and ports are easy to access without removing the case.
  • Flexible wrap-around TPU case offers comfortable grip and easy installation.
  • Slim and compact design provides a snug fit to your device.
  • Built-in covered power and volume button for extra protection.

Specification:

Product Type: TPU Case.

Manufacturer: AMZER.

ACHLA Designs, a Garden Accessories company, emphasizes unique, handforged, wrought iron, European furnishings for the home and garden. Product_Title: Kayak Canoe Wall-Mounted Rack Storage Brackets Swivel Sports Design
Body_Html:
Features:
Space-saving:
The lifting frame can be rotated 90 degrees, so items will block the way when not in use. After being easily folded, you can even remove the extended arm. Help you save garage space.
Sturdy metal parts:
Our metal parts are very strong. Unlike other products, they are plastic parts that are prone to breakage. The screw holes are installed on a straight line. So the kayak frame has a side bracket, which measures 0.78 inches wide by 1.38 inches long. It can be installed on a wall with a minimum width of 2 cm. (0.8 inch)
Material and Capacity:
It adopts heavy steel pipe structure and black rubber cover bracket. Exclusive multi-level anti-rust process. It can hold up to 100 pounds (approximately 45.4 kg).
Storing kayaks and paddles:
The upper bracket arm helps you safely store most sizes of kayaks. The lower hook provides more storage space for paddles or hanging other accessories.
Spring button design:
F tube and L tube are connected by a solid spring button. The hook joint is welded and has good load-bearing performance.

1x Kayak Canoe Wall-Mounted Rack Storage Brackets Swivel Sports Design

Body_Html:
Stylish and modern looking, our Gardeon outdoor storage box is just perfect for storage outdoors and indoors. With a large storage capacity, the box is totally practical in every way. Use it to store anything, from gardening paraphernalia to collectibles to books, clothes or even beddings. Made of durable and weatherproof PP material, the box does not rust and can stand up to robust use with ease. It comes with an aluminium hinge and inner lid stopper for hassle-free use. The integrated handles make it easy to carry it around while the lockable lid helps to keep things safe and secured. Better still, the storage box can also double up as a bench for casual seating anytime. It is also easy to assemble with no tools required.

Outdoor and indoor use
Large storage capacity
Double up as bench seat
Eco-friendly PP material
Lockable lid
Aluminium hinge
Inner lid stopper
Easy to assemble (no tools required)
Weatherproof
Rust-free

Product_Title: Glow in the Dark Blanket & Pillow Set-Gray & Blue
Body_Html: The Glow in the dark blanket throw is multi-functional and can be used to snuggle when watching your favorite program, for sleeping, relaxing, playing and as a throw blanket. The blanket is made with high quality luminous microfiber plush polyester, it is soft, fuzzy, beautiful and very cozy. Expose the glow in the dark blanket under direct sunlight for at least thirty minutes, take it inside to a dark area and see the wonderful color glowing through. The fuzzy blanket is an excellent gift for any occasion for boys, girls and adults can use it as well. It is durable, does not fade or shed. The glow in the dark blanket for boys and blanket for girls can be used all year round, put a smile on your young ones faces with this glow in the dark moon and stars blanket, add an accompanying pillow to make their day and night even more happier. Blanket is Extra Large and the measurement are: 90 X 60 inches, Gray in color, The Dog Pillow is 17 inches and Color is Blue, it lights up when operated with 3AA Batteries (Batteries are NOT included)

Product_Title: Everfit Electric Treadmill 480mm 18kmh 3.5HP Auto Incline Home Gym Run
Body_Html:
Compact and sturdy with its powder-coated steel frame, our Everfit Electric Treadmill allows you to perform essential cardio exercises within the comfort of your home. It features 12 pre-set training programs designed to simulate natural terrain. A user-centric control panel with a digital LCD display lets you set up to 18 speed levels and other monitoring parameters. Its powerful motor produces smooth and seamless operation and the anti-slip belt and soft-grip handlebar with pulse sensors make your session a comfortable and controlled experience. Other great features include a 15-level inclination adjustment, innovative double shock absorption system, automatic motor and belt lubrication, safety tether key, hydraulic fold-down for easy folding and storage, and smooth wheels for easy mobility. Not least, the treadmill is also equipped with USB and MP3 connection, twin speakers and dual drink holders to keep you entertained and hydrated. Best of all, the treadmill has a multifunctional workout system built in with a massage belt, sit-up bar and two dumbbells to allow for more fun and varied exercise.

Important: Running board surface must be checked for lubrication before first use. If it is dry to the touch, then lubrication is needed.

High-strength composite running board
Sturdy powder-coated steel frame
User-centric control panel
Bright digital LCD display
Powerful and energy-efficient motor
Anti-slip and wear-resistant running belt
12 training programs
18 speed levels
15-level auto inclination
Double shock absorption system
Auto belt lubrication
Dual drink holders

Soft-grip handlebar
Foldable design

USB and MP3 connection
Speaker output
Multifunctional workout set: massage belt, sit-up bar, and dumbbells
SAA, CE, RoHS certified

Product_Title: Hyper Fetch Maxi Dog Ball Thrower - Large Interactive Pet Toy Launcher
Body_Html:
The All For Paws Hyper Fetch Dog Toy Maxi provides your dog with plenty of indoor and outdoor fetching fun. The All For Paws Hyper Fetch Dog Toy Maxi is perfect for dogs that have too much energy for you to handle or if you can't throw a ball due to a physical reason, you needn't fear as with this device, fetch time can still stay as your dogs favourite game.

The unit has a rechargeable battery and adjustable distances for the ball to launch so as to suit whatever environment you have available. The adjustable distances are 3, 7.5 and 12 metres and obviously shorter if your dog is quick on the uptake to grab the ball when it launches.

Features

  • Rechargeable Battery
  • Stimulate Dogs Mind- automatic ball launcher challenging them to learn something new. Plays fetch with your dog, interactive features aid in training.
  • Adjustable Distance Settings - make it throw 10ft (3m), 25ft (7.5m) or 40ft (12m). Great training tool for both older dogs and as a way to tire out energetic puppies.
  • Entertain and Exercise - your pet indoors and outside with the all for paws automatic fetch ball launcher, this is the premium choice in automatic fetch games.
  • Ball Launcher Includes - three standard tennis balls, ideal for a game of fetch. Works with 6 pcs C batteries ( not included ), or with AC adapter (included).

Specifications

  • Size: 27cm (height) x 21cm (width) x 26cm (depth)
  • Colour: White and Green
  • Weight: 4.1 kg
  • Package :
    • Comes in original colour box
    • 1 x Hyper Fetch Maxi Device
    • 3 Medium / Standard Size 2.5" Tennis Balls
    • 1 x Au Plug Adapter
    • Instructions Manual

    How to Use

    • First, push the “power on /off button” for 3 seconds to turn the Hyper fetch Maxi on. The “power on/off indicator” (green light) will turn on. To turn off the Hyper Fetch Mini, push the “power on/off button” for another 3 seconds.
    • Secondly, press “power on/off button” to choose the distance 10ft, 20ft or 30ft.
    • Thirdly, put the balls in the ball basket on the top of the Hyper Fetch Maxi. Finally, when balls are placed into the ball basket, the Hyper Fetch Maxi will throw a ball every 10 seconds.
    • There is a tennis ball sensor in the toy. It will scan every 10 seconds. Once detecting the ball, it will trigger the launch system to launch the ball out.

Product_Title: Everfit Electric Treadmill 48cm Incline Running Home Gym Fitness
Body_Html:
Compact and sturdy with its powder-coated steel frame, the Everfit Electric Treadmill allows you to perform essential cardio exercises within the comfort of your home. It features 12 pre-set training programs designed to simulate natural terrain. A user-centric control panel with a digital LCD display lets you set up to 18 speed levels and other monitoring parameters. Its linear power drive motor produces smooth and seamless operation and the anti-slip belt and soft-grip handle bar with pulse sensors make your session a comfortable and controlled experience. Other great features include a 15-level inclination adjustment, innovative double shock absorption system, automatic motor and belt lubrication, safety tether key and smooth wheels for easy mobility. Not least, the electric treadmill is also equipped with a USB and MP3 connection, dual speakers, dual drink holders and a tablet holder for those who like to work out in style.

Important: Running belt must be checked for lubrication before first use. Please refer to manual for details.

Features
High strength composite running board
Sturdy powder coated steel frame
User-centric control panel
Bright digital LCD display
Powerful and energy-efficient motor
Anti-slip and wear-resistant running belt
12 training programs
18 speed levels
15-level auto inclination
Double shock absorption system
Auto Belt lubrication
Dual drink holders
Safety tether key
Soft-grip handle bar
Foldable design
Smooth wheels for mobility
Tablet holder
USB and MP3 connection
Speakers output
SAA, CE, RoHS certified

Specifications:
Running belt size: 125cm x 48cm
Rated voltage: 240V
Rated power: 3.5HP
Speed: 0.8-18KM/H
Programs: 12
Weight capacity: 150kg
Belt thickness: 1.6mm
Board Thickness: 16mm
LCD screen size: 5-inch
Sensor: Speed, time, Distance,Calories,Pulse, mode,start stop,program
Suspension points: 6 point Rubber cushion
Shock Absorption system: Joint support butterfly spring shock control system
Folding system: Hydraulic fold down
Other functions:2 speakers, amplify and MP3 connection, USB input
Colour: Black and white

Package Content
1 x Everfit Electric Treadmill
1 x User Manual
1 x Lubricating Oil

This arrangement creates a dynamic, multi-dimensional effect, adding depth and interest to the displayed art. The panels can be hung in various configurations to suit different spaces and artistic preferences.

Our Play 365 Spike Society Toy is great for everyday games of fetch, but it also doubles as a snuggly naptime friend, and dogs love that!

Product_Title: 3 in 1 Fast Wireless Charger Dock Station US PLUG
Body_Html:
Features:

LED light function

The 3 in 1 table wireless charging dock with a round ring light can light up the darkness. The light brightness and light color can be adjusted as you want.

3 in 1

The 3 in 1 table wireless charging dock with one earphone charging bracket, one smart watch charging bracket and one smart phone charger, can support three device to be charged at same time.

Tidy

The 3 in 1 table wireless charging dock has the back cable groove design to store the charging cable and make your desk tidy without cable mass.

Convenient

The wireless phone charging panel is convenient to operate, without frequently plug. It also can support your phone in vertical direction to display the smart phone when it is not used.

Scope of application

The 3 in 1 table wireless charging dock is widely suitable for home, office, dorm room, shop and so on.


Note:

The earphone charging cable and smart watch charging cable are not included.


Specification:

Type: 3 in 1 table wireless charging dock

Quantity: 1pc

Material: ABS+ PVC + electric component

Color: white / black

Plug: EU/ US

Voltage:

US 110-220V

Input: 9v/ 3.5a

Wireless output: 5-7.5-10w

USB output: 5v/ 1a

Led power: 0.1-6w

Light source: 114pcs LED beads

Sensor distance: 2-6mm

Working frequency: 100-205khz

Convert rate: 73%

Size: 30*9.5*32.5cm/ 11.79*3.73*12.77inch(L*W*H)

Net weight: 675g/ 23.81oz


Package:

1* 3 in 1 table wireless charging dock

Cannot ship to PO boxes.

Product_Title: Pop it fidget toys Game For Adult Kid Push Bubble Fidget Sensory Toy
Body_Html:
Features:

The product is made of high-quality food-grade silicone and has obtained relevant quality inspection certificates. non-toxic and tasteless, and can be cleaned with boiling water. A variety of bright colors are easy to get the favorite of children.
When you press the bubble, there will be a slight "pop" sound. After the game is over, you can turn the toy over to start the next round of the game.
It can be used for kids to exercise the child's ability to grasp objects. When children play, they can exercise their logical thinking and calculation skills.

Style:please see the pictures.

Game Rules:
Players take turns to press the bubbles. Each player can press 1-3 bubbles at a time, and must press the connected bubbles each time. If the player cannot press the bubble, it means the player has lost.
You can also customize the game rules according to the situation.
After the toy is flipped, the next round of the game can be played.

Product_Title: Electric 36 Egg Incubator - Poultry Chicken Duck Quail Turkey Birds
Body_Html:
Automatic 36 Egg Incubator.

Including an auto turning tray, hatchery days count, and Electric LED Digital screen, our egg incubators are fully certified CE EMC ECM CNAS SAA, made with high industry standards,  and highly durable. With a simple and smart digital design, anyone can use our egg incubators easily.

Our EGG Incubator Features Include

  • EGG Candler Light Tester Included in package
  • Display for Countdown of days remaining before eggs hatch (2 hours units)
  • Smart design with streamlined shape for ease of use
  • Made for beginners as well as professionals
  • High industry standards & trusted certificates
  • Automatic digital display
  • Temperature & humidity display
  • Temperature and humidity automatic functions (35-40 Degrees Celsius)
  • Temperature and humidity advanced manual control (temperature range 0~99 degrees Celsius)
  • Automatic egg turning motor
  • Quality PP material with a solid moulded construction
  • Anti-jamming function and higher stability
  • Clear cover for egg visibility; allows easy observation
  • Automatic cooling and ventilating system
  • Long service life
  • CE certified
  • ECM approved
  • EMC certified
  • SAA approved
  • CNAS tested and certified
  • Australian electrical standards with AU plug
  • Voltage: 220-240V
  • Frequency: 50-60Hz
  • Assembled Size: height 30cm x length 53cm x width 52cm

This Egg Incubator's capacity includes any one of the following

  • 36 chicken eggs
  • 36 duck
  • 36 turkey eggs
  • 144 quail size / bird eggs

What is an Egg Candler Tester? (included)

An egg candler is a device used for testing eggs. Candling eggs is a method of testing eggs while they are incubating to determine if they are viable or not. "Viable" means that the egg is fertilised and an embryo is able to develop and hatch. So make sure when you buy your egg incubator to have an Egg Tester Included in the package which we have in all our egg incubators.

Product_Title: Rotate The Ball At Your Fingertips Desktop Toy
Body_Html:
Overview:

  - It is a precision machined desk toy that creates a mesmerizing optical illusion when spun. Simply rotate it to reveal the mind-bending effect of a continuously flowing helix. 

    - A piece of art that invites you to transform it from a precisely engineered still shape into a hypnotic optical illusion. 

    - When revolving, it creates an almost magical effect that looks like a continuously flowing helix would merge into a surface of the tabletop. 

    - It is designed to spin on any desk or flat surface. The solid body and smooth finish make it very pleasant to interact with. It spins silently so you won't be bothering anyone around.

Product_Title: Tropical Fish Finger Puppet (light pink and yellow)
Body_Html:
ThumbThings Finger Puppets Are Fun To Collect, Trade, And Share With Your Friends!!

Our eco-friendly, sustainably made, Clown Fish finger puppet has been hand crafted by artisan collectives from the rural areas of the Peruvian high-plains. We source ethically, practice fair trade principles and strive to help these artisans extend their products reach. As descendants of the Incas, these artisans, mostly women, have been working with textiles for generations. Knitting is a proud tradition for the Quechua and Aymara people who still use traditional methods today. Most work from home using their passion and skills to create these colorful finger puppets which help supplement their family's income. 

Each finger puppet is as unique as the artist who created it! Some characters are only available in limited quantities and then never made again. Others are created by artisans from subsistence communities who only knit during certain periods of the year and produce small quantities of magnificent finger puppets. Our network of artisan-producers is comprised of over 800 talented individuals who are encouraged to use their creativity to the fullest! These toys are special, they are not made in a factory, they are handmade with love! 

Kids are spending more time than ever in front of screens, and child development experts, along with concerned adults, worry that electronic gadgets might substitute for important interaction. Learning through play is a vital aspect of childhood, and experts say your child should be encouraged to do so every day. Finger Puppets help promote a wide range of developmental aspects. The simple act of offering your child a few finger puppets can do wonders for their language, social-emotional, cognitive and physical development. Best of all, they aren’t just for children, ThumbThings Handmade Finger Puppets bring out the kid in all of us!

Certified by Green America, GreenP% For The Planet. Fair Trade, Handmade and Eco-Friendly! Ages 3+ 100% Nylon yarn and polyfill stuffing, all new materials. Gently hand wash, do not machine dry.

The handcrafted touch of artisan skill creates variations in color, size and design. If buying two of the same item, slight differences should be expected. Note: Color discrepancies may occur between this product and your computer screen.

  • 100% Nylon yarn with poly-fill stuffing, all new materials.

  • Recommended for Ages 3+

  • This is a handmade product.

  • Over 200 different characters to collect, trade, and share.

  • No two finger puppets are exactly alike each is unique in its own way.

Collect Them A!!!

There are over 200 adorable characters to play with, collect, trade, and share! Finger puppets excite the imagination, and inspire creativity in kids, they will will put down their electronic gadgets and spend hours interacting and playing pretend games with each other, all while learning valuable social skills!

Product_Title: Keezi 24 Piece Kids Super Market Toy Set - Red & White
Body_Html:
Supermarket Pretend Play Set

Featuring a colourful supermarket pretend play set with 24pcs accessories, this pretend play set is perfect for kids to perform shopping role plays with friends and parents. The play set comes with a mini trolley allowing kids to role play as a customer. Also, included a barcode scanner with sound and lighting features; just like a real one! While the play set provides plenty of fun during play, it is also an excellent educational learning play set for kids; encouraging teamwork, communication, expression and logic exercises. Let's bring this fun and creative supermarket pretend play set home for your loving ones.

Features

* Colourful design with 24pcs accessories
* Lighting and sound features
* Battery operated (not included)
* Recommended age 3 years above
* Adult supervision recommended at all times
* Flat packed and easy to assemble with assemble guide
* EN71 European Safety of Toys certified
* Material: Plastic
* Accessory: 24pcs
* Battery required: 2 x AA (not included)
* Product care: Wipe with a clean cloth occasionally
* Counter size: 48x41x82cm
* Trolley size: 35.5x20x40.5cm
* Colour: Red & white

Package Contents

* 1 x Supermarket Pretend Play Set

Product_Title: Squishy Face Studio Tug Toy
Body_Html:
At Last, Soft, Tough Tug Toys For Dogs To Play Tug Of War Without Harmful Rope Strands

Introducing the Tug Toy from Squishy Face Studio. Made of 100% polyester webbing, it is extremely durable, resistant to the outdoor elements, and machine washable.

With a triple layer handle at one end, 6 tassels, and an overall length of about 12.5 inches, it makes the perfect toy for your furry friends that love to play tug-of-war. The Tug Toy can also be purchased as a replacement for the one included with our Super Tug toy.

Body_Html:
About Height Adjustable Piano Stand

  1. Safe and reliable keyboard placement: For a secure and dependable placement of your keyboard, use the 5 Core keyboard stand rack. The piano keyboard stand has a reliable lock mechanism that ensures maximum stability and safety, making it ideal for beginners, amateurs, and performers or musicians.
  2. Unique Z-frame: If you are looking for an Height Adjustable Piano Stand to align your piano or keyboard to your liking, the Z-style stand is a great choice. Its unique design allows for adjustment not only in height but also in width, making it a versatile option for different piano or keyboard sizes.
  3. Anti Scratch arms: To prevent your keyboard from slipping and to safeguard it against scratches or gashes, this keyboard stand comes with padded arms that offer a soft surface for your keyboard to rest on. These pads are also responsible for holding your keyboard securely in place as you play.
  4. Adjustable width: Unlike any other keyboard piano stands that are only adjustable in fixed adjustments, this keyboard stands width is infinitely adjustable. Its sliding lock allows you to adjust the stand, providing greater flexibility in setting up your keyboard.

  5. Designed for travel & storage: Whether you plan to use it at home, in the studio, classroom, or on stage, this Z-style keyboard stand is portable and easy to store. It can be folded into a compact Z-shape for effortless transport and storage, and setting it up takes less than a minute.
Height Adjustable Piano Stand Description

Experience the ultimate in a keyboard stand technology with our top-of-the-line product. Boasting a secure stability lock mechanism, rugged organ mount rack, and padded arms, our keyboard stand offers maximum stability and protection for your keyboard. The 5 Core keyboard stand is also incredibly versatile thanks to its unique Z frame design, which allows for easy height and width adjustment.

With its infinitely adjustable width and sliding lock mechanism, you will have complete control over the placement of your keyboard. Whether you're a beginner, amateur, or professional musician, our Height Adjustable Piano Stand is designed to meet your needs. Plus, with its easy setup, breakdown, and compact, portable design, you can take it wherever you go.


At 5 Core, Customer satisfaction is our priority—a proven track record of delivering the highest quality product since 1984.

Universal

Made From Steel

Portable

Padded Arm

It can be used with instruments from 54 to 61 keys and turntables, mixers, MIDI keyboards, and other instruments.

Crafted from sturdy steel, the 5 Core keyboard piano stand is built to last. Its intelligent design ensures it can withstand the demands of even the most active mobile musician while being comfortable in a home environment.

Thanks to its portable design, the 5 Core keyboard stand is easy to set up and pack away. You can have it ready to go in just a minute, allowing you to focus on what really matters- playing your instrument.

The 5 Core Z-shaped keyboard stand features pads on the top, adding an extra layer of stability and protecting your keyboard piano from scratches and damage.

The panels can be hung in various configurations to suit different spaces and artistic preferences.

Product_Title: Crawling Crab Interactive Toy
Body_Html:
Natural Pet Stimulation!

The interactive Crawling Crab™ Dog Toy is PAWFECT for play time with the doggos! It can help keep your fur-baby both mentally & physically stimulated for HOURS!!

Contact Motion Sensor!

The Crawling Crab™ Dog Toy has a silent contact motion sensor! It automatically stops crawling once it detects an obstacle & resumes crawling in the opposite direction for continuous play time for your doggo!

Doggos Are Loving The Crawling Crab!

Looking for the PAWfect present for your doggo? Join over 25,000+ happy doggos that are loving the Crawling Crab™ Dog Toy!

Safe For Your Fur Baby!

The Crawling Crab™ Doggo Toy has durable TPR-Grade & ABS material that's designed to withstand strong chewers! It's been trialed & tested 1000's of times to ensure that it can be safe for your pet to play with!

Child Friendly!

The interactive design of the Crawling Crab™ is both engaging and safe for your child and dogs to play with - making play time fun for the entire family!

Rechargeable Battery!

The Crawling Crab™ has a USB-Rechargeable battery that can last for up to 2 days of fun time for your doggos! It also comes with a complementary USB charging cable that can connect to any USB-Based Device!

Product_Title: 5Core Outdoor Speakers Stereo In Wall 400W Peak Passive Patio Home
Body_Html:
About Item

  1. Designed to live indoors & outdoors: These speakers are versatile and designed for both indoor and outdoor use. They can be placed or mounted in any open space, such as on a bookshelf, under your patio, in the garage, or by the pool. Regardless of placement, they will deliver extraordinary sound and have a maximum output power of 800W(combined) RMS- 80W(Combined). The mounting type for these speakers is a wall mount.
  2. Digitally Optimized: The 5 Core Wall Speakers are digitally optimized for expansive dispersion and powerful bass. When synchronized, these speakers create a state of accurate acoustic dispersion with deep, rich-sounding bass, resulting in a truly full range of sound.
  3. Effortless mounting swivel brackets: Effortless mounting is possible and can be mounted in a matter of seconds in any open space and provide a range of high-fidelity sound.
  4. All-weather resistant coating: These wall speakers are made to withstand every season, as they are coated with UV-resistant resin and placed inside an PP enclosure. This weather-resistant coating protects them from the elements while preserving sound integrity.
  5. Engineered for great sound: Engineered for great sound, the wall speakers utilize a high excursion speaker that can be aimed to project a spacious sound stage. This amazing speaker system is well-suited for a range of applications.

Product Description

Introducing our extraordinary 5 Core Speakers, the perfect sound solution for any indoor or outdoor space. Designed with versatility in mind, these speakers can be placed or mounted anywhere, from your bookshelf to your poolside, delivering powerful sound with a maximum output power of 800W. These speakers are digitally optimized for expansive dispersion and powerful bass, creating a full range of sound that will captivate your senses. With effortless mounting swivel brackets, you can easily install these speakers in seconds, and enjoy a range of high-fidelity sound. Made to withstand every season, these speakers feature an all-weather-resistant coating that protects them from the elements while preserving sound integrity. Experience great sound like never before with our 5 Core Speakers.At 5 Core, Customer satisfaction is our priority—a proven track record of delivering the highest quality product since 1984.

Features

Easy Installation

Weather Resistant

Versatile Orientation

High Quality Audio

Installing these Wall Speakers is a breeze mark, and cut the mounting hole with a drywall knife. The built-in mounting tabs securely grab onto the surrounding drywall, requiring only a screwdriver to install.

With a weather-resistant design, these speakers are perfect for use on covered porches, outdoor patios, lanais, or gazebos. They are specially designed to withstand rain and heat, so you can enjoy your favorite music in any weather condition.

The orientation of your Wall Speakers is versatile, as they can be mounted either horizontally or vertically to fit any space better.

These Wall Speakers are specially designed for high-quality audio and built to maximize your listening experience. Your sound will come out crisp and clear, delivering an exceptional listening experience.

Technical Specifications:

  • Max. Power 400W Each
  • RMS 40W Each
  • Frequency Response 70Hz-20Khz
  • Operated at 100V/70V
  • SPL at 1 kHz 92dB ±2dB
  • Speaker 5.25

Package includes:

  • 2x Wall speaker

About Brand

Core, headquartered in California, warehouse in Bellefontaine, OH, USA, has a reputation for being a trusted and reliable brand, offering products designed to meet the highest industry standards. Our products are thoroughly tested and inspected before they are sent to the end user, ensuring that the customers receive products of the highest quality and reliability. With a commitment to quality, affordability, and customer satisfaction, 5 Core is a brand people can trust for all their needs and wants.

I swear it only takes about 20 minutes to assemble the Pipe Shelves with Wood Planks as long as you follow the instructions properly and the gravity where you live is still working.

Product_Title: 10kg Automatic Chook Chicken Feeder Poultry Auto Treadle Galvanised
Body_Html:
This Embossed Aluminium and Galvanised Steel Automatic Chicken Feeder provides a protected way of feeding your backyard chickens on demand. The lid can be opened when chickens (minimum 500g) step onto the platform. This clever design allows chickens to access their food when hungry, hence training them to self feed.

Specifications:

  • Model: CF-07
  • Feed Volume: 10Kg
  • Weight: 3.9Kg
  • Material: Galvanised Steel
  • Colour: Silver
  • Size (cm): 51(L) x 37(H) x 40.5(W)

Features:

  • Rust-proof and waterproof galvanised steel
  • Keeps feed dry
  • Trains chickens to self feed
  • Solid construction and long lasting
  • 500 grams weight can open the lid
  • Suitable for poultry and birds
  • Protective film
  • Keeps feed clean and fresh
  • Prevents little wild birds, rats and mice (weight below 500 g) stealing feed
  • Water proof, saves valuable feed from rain
  • Saves on feed costs, no more wasted or stolen feed
  • Easy to assemble and low maintenance
  • Large capacity can hold up to 10kg of feed
  • Suitable for most bantams

Package Includes:

  • 1x 10kg Feed Galvanised Steel Chicken Feeder Treadle
  • Accessories and Instructions

Note: Needs assembly

Product_Title: ROCKROOSTER Edgewood Men's 6 inch Brown soft toe wedge work boots
Body_Html:
ROOSTER Wedge Work Boots for Men, 6" Soft Toe Water Resistant Industrial & Construction Work Boots, Safety Water Resist Leather Boots, Electrical Shock protection ASTM F2892-18 EH, AP838
  • 【Soft Toe】
  • 【Dual Density PU Outsole】slip, chemical, acid resistant outsole, comfortable and durable
  • 【Electrical Shock protection】 ASTM F2892-18 EH compliant, electrical work boots protection against shock up to 18000V
  • 【PORON Materials】With Microban technology provide consistent, reliable and long-lasting protection to your wedge work boots.
  • 【CoolMAX】Temperature Control, Moisture Wicking, Quick Dry.
  • 【Oiled Crazy Horse Leather】high quality performance leather that is water resistant and durable.
  • 【Width 】Normal (E), width is a indication of the space in the ball of the boots. Give your toes more space so they do not feel cramped. For exact measurement please refer to the size chart.
  • 【Safety Rating 】ASTM F2892-18 EH
  • Size in men's size, for women's size simply add 1.5. IE Men's US 6 would be equivalent of Women's US 7.5

VAP838 Upgrade:

  • 【Vibram® Outsole】Manufactured with Vibram® outsole, which is known for its outstanding traction, durability and uniform texture combined with our anti fatigue foam insole allowing maximum traction and cushion in excessive work.
  • PU wedge outsole
  • Shaft measures approximately 5.25'' from arch
  • Platform measures approximately .75"

Product_Title: 5 Core Compression Driver 400W Peak Aluminium Tweeter Diaphragm 16 Ohm
Body_Html:
Experience Crystal-Clear Highs with- Compression Driver Speaker

  1. High Performance Compression Driver 400W PMPO, 40W RMS projects loud, clear, and far-reaching audio.

  2. Wide 160- 7000 Hz Frequency Response delivering clear, detailed audio across various musical ranges.

  3. 16 Ohm Impedance and Universal 18 T.P.I threading ensure compatibility across different audio setup.

  4. Durable Aluminum construction with Y30 ferrite magnet for consistent, reliable performance over time

  5. Weatherproof horn tweeters ensures continuous audio projection indoors & outdoors in any conditions.


Compression Driver Speaker Description

Experience the ultimate in audio fidelity with our mid range speaker compression driver! Boasting an impressive R.M.S. power of 40W and a peak power of 400W, it delivers crisp, clear sound across a wide frequency response of 160-7000 Hz. Designed with a sturdy Y 30 Ferrite Magnet and durable aluminum construction, it’s both powerful and long-lasting.


With a weatherproof build, it’s ready for any environment. The compression driver’s universal 18 T.P.I. threading ensures easy integration with different horn throats. Whether for studio setup or outdoor events, this 16- Ohm driver provides the perfect balance of power, reliability, and exceptional sound quality.

Compression Driver Speaker Features

Loud Clear Sound

Heavy Duty Construction

Better Compatibility

Easy Installation

Premium compression driver reproduces audio with exceptional clarity, balanced tones, and minimal distortion.

Durable build quality, made of high-grade aluminum to withstand regular use without degradation in performance.

16 Ohms impedance rating is vastly compatible with a wide range of amplifiers, receivers, or other audio setups.

Compression tweeter horn with 4 inch depth and 4 inch width, 18 TPI threading simplifies installation.

Horn Tweeter Specification:

  • RMS Power: 40 Watt
  • Max Power: 60 Watt
  • PMPO Power: 400 Watt
  • Frequency Response: 160- 7000 Hz
  • Impedance Rating: 16 Ohms
  • Magnet Type: Y 30 Ferrite Magnet
  • Material: Aluminium 
  • Weatherproof: Yes
  • Threading: Universal 18 T.P.I
  • Weight: 3.2 Lb

  • Temperature and humidity advanced manual control (temperature range 0~99 degrees Celsius)
  • Automatic egg turning motor
  • Quality PP material with a solid moulded construction
  • Anti-jamming function and higher stability
  • Clear cover for egg visibility; allows easy observation
  • Automatic cooling and ventilating system
  • Long service life
  • CE certified
  • ECM approved
  • EMC certified
  • SAA approved
  • CNAS tested and certified
  • Australian electrical standards with AU plug
  • Voltage: 220-240V
  • Frequency: 50-60Hz
  • Assembled Size: height 30cm x length 53cm x width 52cm

This Egg Incubator's capacity includes any one of the following

  • 60 chicken eggs
  • 30 duck eggs
  • 30 turkey eggs
  • 100 quail size / bird eggs

What is an Egg Candler Tester? (included)

An egg candler is a device used for testing eggs. Candling eggs is a method of testing eggs while they are incubating to determine if they are viable or not. "Viable" means that the egg is fertilised and an embryo is able to develop and hatch. So make sure when you buy your egg incubator to have an Egg Tester Included in the package which we have in all our egg incubators.

Product_Title: 5 Core Keyboard Stand Riser • Double Braced X Style Adjustable Width
Body_Html:
MIXER STAND


About Item


  1. Adjustable Height with Position Clutch: 7 holes correlate to 7 heights. To fix it, Equipped with a rigid clamping system, raise the legs to the right height, align, and put the lock pin into the nearest hole. The keyboard stand can be adjusted to hold the keyboard at a height that allows for standing keyboard performance or at a lower height for bench-style seating. Die Casted Piece for proper alignment of pipes.

  2. Double Braced Heavy Duty X-Style Legs: Dual X-shaped frames are used in the design of this adjustable keyboard stand to add stability and longevity. For long-term use and Uncompromising Durability, reinforced welds can withstand repeated movement. Non-slip rubber end caps add extra stability. Quick-release mechanism allows the user to adjust the height, compared to most other stands, which only permit five set positions.

  3. Non-slip Rubber Caps: The legs are constructed with heavy-duty steel pipe, and each end has fixed rubber caps. These caps ensure optimum stability while you are performing. It eliminates the chance of slipping and accidental falls.

  4. Strongest in the US market: Heavy Duty Steel Tubes measuring 2.5 cm square and 0.8 mm thick are used to build the 5 Core keyboard stand, ensuring enough strength and durability. Heavy-duty double-x metal construction ensures extra stability for heavy and light digital electronic keyboards. Three-legged structure for proper balancing & quick operation.

  5. No Assembly Needed: No assembly is needed before usage; metal parts are welded together, and no screws to lose. Durable materials are used to ensure long-term strength. Most major keyboard brands would benefit from this giftable addition. The stand is the best option whether you are an amateur or a professional. This heavy-duty keyboard stand folds up easily. This Keyboard Stand comes fully assembled and ready to use! Instead of wasting time building a keyboard stand, use that time to jam!


Product Description

Looking for the MOST sturdy and reliable stand to hold your piano or keyboard in the USA market? Look no further than the 5 Core Pre-Assembled Digital Piano Bench. Whether you are a beginner or a professional musician, this double X-style bench is the perfect accessory for your keyboard, piano, and other instruments. With its adjustable height and position clutch system, you can easily adjust the stand to hold your keyboard at the perfect height for your performance.

The double-braced X-style legs provide extra stability and durability, reinforced with welds that can withstand repeated movement. The non-slip rubber end caps prevent the stand from slipping or sliding or slipping during the event of the most intense performance. Additionally, the non-slip rubber caps ensure that your keyboard stays securely in place, while the heavy-duty steel tubes can support both heavy and light digital electronic keyboards. The 5 Core keyboard stand comes fully assembled and ready to use, so you can start playing immediately.


At 5 Core, Customer satisfaction is our priority—a proven track record of delivering the highest quality product since 1984.


Features

Folding for Easy Storage

Non-slip Feet

Double-X Frame

Heavy Duty Steel Tubes

The stand can be easily folded when not in use, allowing it to take up minimal space. This feature makes it effortless to store or transport the stand whenever needed.

The non-slip feet caps are designed to rotate, preventing the stand from moving around and protecting the floor. These caps ensure that the stand remains stable and secure during use.

The 5 Core X-style keyboard stand is constructed with a heavy-duty, sturdy X frame. This design ensures that the stand can support almost any keyboard without movement or damage. 

5 Core keyboard stand is constructed with 2.5cm square tubing 0.8mm thick steel, which ensures sufficient strength and sturdiness.

Product specification:

  • Total height 100 cm

  • Open Height 64 cm

  • Weight 10.35 Lbs.


The package comes with the following:

  • 1x Keyboard stand

  • 1x Carrying bag


Usages

Use the stand to secure your keyboard or piano.

Play your keyboard or piano in a comfortable position.

Take the stand with you and set it up at your convenience.

Rotate the non-slip feet caps to keep the stand stable on any surface.

Set up the stand on stage or during live performance easily & effortlessly.



Benefits of products

Folds flat for easy storage & transport.

Lightweight design for easy portability.

Easy to adjust the stand to your desired height.

Adjustable height helps you to improve posture.

It prevents your keyboard or piano from slipping or moving around.



Benefits of 5 Core over other products


Durable and sturdy design, it is built to last.

Well compatible with most keyboards and pianos.

Saves time & effort by providing a quick & easy setup.

Designed for added stability and security during use.

Non-slip feet caps prevent the stand from moving around & protect the floor.



Why 5 Core

5 Core has been known for producing high-quality, premium products since 1984.

We are committed to using only the best materials and components to ensure the longevity of our products.

The best deals compared to other brands in the market without compromising on quality.

The trustworthy choice for thousands of customers scattered worldwide in more than 65 countries.

Backed by a proven track record of happy customers and peace of mind.

5 Core, headquartered in California, warehouse in Bellefontaine, OH, USA, has a reputation for being a trusted and reliable brand, offering products designed to meet the highest industry standards. Our products are thoroughly tested and inspected before they are sent to the end user, ensuring that the customers receive products of the highest quality and reliability. With a commitment to quality, affordability, and customer satisfaction, 5 Core is a brand people can trust for all their needs and wants

Question: Is the keyboard stand easy to assemble?

Answer: Yes, the keyboard stand is easy to assemble, and it comes with a hex wrench and screws that are required for the assembly.

Question: Can the X-stand be adjusted for different heights?

Answer: Yes, the X stand is designed to be adjustable with 5 different height options, making it comfortable to use while sitting or standing.

Question: How stable is the stand during use?

Answer: The stand is designed with a double X frame, reinforced welds, and rubber pads that provide maximum stability during use.

Question: Is the stand portable?

Answer: Yes, the X stand is lightweight and can be easily folded for convenient storage and transport, making it ideal for on-the-go musicians.

Answer: Yes, it is heavy-duty stand.

Body_Html:
InnovaGoods is here to help you make cooking easy and fun by offering you the best new items for your kitchen, such as the Compact Knife Sharpener Knedhger InnovaGoods ! Discover a wide range of high-quality items that stand out for their functionality, efficiency and innovative design!

A very practical, safe and effective way to sharpen knives. It allows for different types and forms of sharpening, to achieve the perfect result with ease and comfort. Furthermore, given its small size, thanks to its compact design, it takes up very little space.

  • Materials: ABS
  • Material:
    • Steel
    • Tungsten
    • Ceramic
  • Colour:
    • Black
    • Silver
  • Modern and ergonomic design: Innovative and functional
  • Type: Manual sharpener
  • Characteristics: Non-slip base
  • 2 sharpening grooves:

    • Ceramic: for final polishing and daily sharpening for maintenance

Product_Title: Multi Plug Outlet Extender Power Travel Adapter Wall Plug 3/4 USB Cube
Body_Html:
UTA W 


About Item


  1. Worldwide adapter: The 5 Core travel adapter is a versatile travel accessory that works in over 150 countries, with compatibility for US, EU, AU, and UK plug types. However, please note that it is not a voltage converter.

  2. Four USB Ports: With four USB ports, this universal travel adapter can charge a variety of devices, including phones, tablets, laptops, cameras, and sales from popular brands.

  3. 4 In-1 Input: Save space and time with 4 in 1 input design, allowing you to charge four devices simultaneously without carrying multiple chargers. Its compact size makes it a convenient option for travel.

  4. Certified and Safety: Safety is a top priority with this international plug adapter, which is FCC, CE, and RoHS certified with a built-in 6.3 Amp fuse for complete protection. 

  5. The Brand Promise: The 5 Core brand offers extensive support for the products as a top-selling travel adapter brand. Experience the best travel experience and keep your devices charged up all time with our power adapter.


Product Description

Are you tired of packing multiple chargers for your travels? Look no further than the 5 Core international power adapter! With compatibility in over 150 countries and an all-in-one design, this travel companion is the perfect solution for any adventurer.

Charge all your devices at once with the four USB ports, including popular brands. And with its compact size, you won't have to sacrifice valuable suitcase space. Certified and built-in safety standards ensure the safety of you and your devices.


At 5 Core, Customer satisfaction is our priority—a proven track record of delivering the highest quality product since 1984.


Features

Multifunctional Travel Plug

Multiple Protections

Travel & Cruise Friendly

Automatic Surge Protective Fuse

This International Travel Adapter can use 4 USBs at the same time. The 5 Core European travel plug adapter is the safest way to plug in your portable, non-grounded devices around the world.

Built-in safety shutter, anti-single plug-in, anti-electric shock. More safety when used. FCC, CE, and RoHS certified with a built-in 6.3 Amp fuse for complete protection.

Only 5.5oz weight. 5 Core universal travel adapter with USB is just about a size of a Rubik cube and will fit well in your backpack and luggage. You can take it anywhere you want

When the power adapter is overloading, the fuse will automatically turn off to protect the circuit and your devices. A few minutes later, the fuse will automatically recover when it cools down and can be used again; no need to manually replace it.

Product specification:


  • Fuse: 6.3 Amp

  • Color: White

  • USB Output: 5V- 3A

  • Max Power: 880W at 110Vac / 1840W at 230Vac 3. Input: 100-240Vac 50/60Hz 

  • Total Output: 5Vdc 5.6A Max 

  • Single USB: 5Vdc 2.4A Max 

  • Fuse Rating: 8A Max 


Package includes: 

  • 1x plug adapter

Power up your portable charger or power bank for extended use.

Powering gaming console or other devices while on a foreign tour.

Charging your phone, tablet, or laptop while travelling internationally.

Connecting & charging a camera or other electronic device while on vacation.

Using your personal hair dryer or straightener in a foreign country with different plug types.

Product_Title: 5Core Desk Mic Stand 2Pcs Adjustable Table Tripod Portable Desktop
Body_Html:
About Desk Mic Stand

  1. Mini Desktop Microphone Stand: The table mic stand's head features a 360-degree rotatable design, allowing for easy adjustment of the microphones to achieve the desired position.
  2. Stable Tripod Leg Base: The mic stand features a stable tripod leg base with anti-slip rubber caps, providing superior stability and protecting the desk from unwanted scratches. 
  3. Adjustable Angle: The mic holder attached to the tripod stand is highly flexible. The angle can be adjusted to 180 degrees to suit your preferences.
  4. Sturdy and Lightweight: The desk stand combines stainless steel and durable ABS for toughness and lightness. Its steel pipe, coated with anti-corrosion paint, enhances longevity through thoughtful design.
  5. Compact and Travel-Friendly: Featuring a collapsible design, our tabletop mic stand effortlessly disassembles into two parts for quick and easy storage.

Microphone Stand Description

Our desktop stand is made from high-quality stainless steel and durable plastic and offers unparalleled performance and reliability. Its rotatable head allows for effortless microphone adjustment, ensuring you find the perfect position for your recording.

The desk mic holder features an external 5/8 inch thread, and you can attach different mics directly to the tripod or accessories. The collapsible and compact design makes the table mic holder easy to carry. Whether performing live or recording in the studio, our foldable microphone tripod stand is the versatile solution you need for flawless audio every time.

Mic Stand Extra Features

Spring Loaded Clip

More Stable

Tough build quality

Easy to Assemble

The microphone clip is unique and adjustable, thanks to its built-in spring. The mic holder supports a wide range of recording and pencil mics.

Engineered with a sturdy tripod base, our desk mic stand ensures your microphone stays in place, no matter the recording or speaking situation.

The ABS base and mic clip are sturdy yet lightweight. There is no chance of rust or water-related damage. It can withstand extreme uses.

The table mic stand is 2 parted, and it has a screw-in style installation process, which takes less than a minute to assemble and doesn’t require any tools.

Microphone Stand Specification: 

  • Color: Black
  • Base Type: Tripod
  • Max Height: 6.3 Inches
  • Material: Steel & Plastic 
  • Angle Adjustment: 180 Degrees

Package Information:

  • 2x Table Mic Stand

About Brand

5 Core, ISO Certified headquartered in California, warehouse in Ohio, USA. Offering 600+ products since 1984. Tested and Certified Products, ensuring highest quality and reliability.

Looking for a different desk mic stand? We have a wide range of Desktop Microphone Stand! Get what you need.
